=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: The Afterlife philosophy</span><hr size=1> I have to agree with the numbers.  In fact my favorite places are the ones with the can't run to zone mentality.  Duke it out.  The best experiences so far for me are the ones where we were overwhelmed.  Talk about adrenaline rush, and then you see the leaders come out and the quick thinkers.  <br>
<br>
As a monk I hate being told to wait on mana as I know we can survive an encounter.  Constant pulls, holding stuff in mez cycles and conserving health by switching aggro on tanks etc.  Something with a little more skill than 1 damage abosrber 1 healer one mob with a full group.  Anyone who's grouped with me on better occasions knows that I like to pull hard enough and fast enough, that the occasional corpse rot happens cause no one has time to loot.<br>
<br>
However, the majority of players never push the envelope and never get to find out just how much they can do.<br>
<br>
One example I had was a group of 4 with an underlevel paladin as the only healer, no nukers and we pulled non-stop for 6 hrs.  We never saw more than 50% health after zone in, but it was a blast. <p>Lacki Dasmacki
41 Monk of the Silent Fist Clan
Mithaniel Marr</p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub18.ezboard.com/fmithanielmarrdailynewsgeneral.showMessage?topicID=750.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub18.ezboard.com/fmithanielmarrdailynewsgeneral.showMessage?topicID=756.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub18.ezboard.com/fmithanielmarrdailynewsgeneral.emailToFriend?topicID=575.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub18.ezboard.com/fmithanielmarrdailynewsgeneral.threadControl?topicID=575.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub18.ezboard.com/fmithanielmarrdailynewsgeneral.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=575.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub18.ezboard.com/fmithanielmarrdailynewsgeneral.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=575.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub18.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="mithanielmarrdailynewsgeneral">NewsRoom<option value="mithanielmarrdailynewsfrm11">Editorials & Rants<option value="mithanielmarrdailynewsfrm23">Sports / Raids<option value="mithanielmarrdailynewsfrm26">Who's Who?<option value="mithanielmarrdailynewsguildsofmithanielmarr">Guild Directory<option value="mithanielmarrdailynewsfrm8">Commerce<option value="mithanielmarrdailynewsroleplayforum">RPers' Corner<